"You heard the gent!" Devilcat calls to the Rogues.  "Come in at a 45 
degree angle to the Pred forces and let 'em have it!"  The cloaked 
formation sweeps around to the oblique vector, looking to catch any 
emerging Maximals in a crossfire.

Pumpskin would have preferred to just dash right in, but he complies 
with Hydras's command, transforming to robot mode and preparing to do 
battle.
